---
import Svg from "@jasikpark/astro-svg-loader";
import { Trans } from "astro-i18next/components";
import { t } from "i18next";

const { CCI_PHONE } = import.meta.env;
const years = new Date().getFullYear() - 2014;
---

<section class="relativepx-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-sm py-32 sm:max-w-[34rem] sm:py-48 lg:py-56">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">
        {t("hero.title")}
        <span
          data-messages={[
            t("hero.list.apartament"),
            t("hero.list.car"),
            t("hero.list.carpet"),
            t("hero.list.garden"),
            t("hero.list.office"),
            t("hero.list.commercial"),
          ]}
          id="typed"
          class="border-b-4 border-amber-500">{t("hero.list.apartament")}</span
        >
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8 text-gray-600">
        <Trans i18nKey="hero.subtitle" />
        Cu o experiență de peste {years} ani în oferirea serviciilor de curațenie, avem un record impresionant de satisfacție
        a clienților de 98%. Suntem dedicați să oferim servicii de curățenie de cea mai înaltă calitate.
        <!-- Oferim servicii de curatenie de peste 7 ani. 98% din clientii nostri sunt multumiti de serviciile noastre. -->
        <!-- More than five years of providing home cleaning services. 98% of our customers are satisfied with our
          services. -->
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
        <a
          href={`tel:${CCI_PHONE}`}
          class="flex items-center rounded-md bg-amber-400 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-amber-300 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-amber-400"
        >
          <Svg src={import("../assets/imgs/phone.svg?raw")} class="w-4 h-4 inline-block fill-white mr-2" />
          {t("common.phone")}</a
        >
        <a href="#cum-functioneaza" class="space-x-2 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
          <Svg src={import("../assets/imgs/eye.svg?raw")} class="w-4 h-4 inline-block fill-gray-900 mr-2" />
          {t("hero.see_more")}<span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
